channel.title: Can't install mods with 1.0.10
channel.description: Just updated to the new version (1.0.10) and tried installing the Permaday mod, which IS compatible with the EA version I'm using, but when I click install I just get a spinner that spins and spins forever and the mod never gets installed. I have to close SML to get my mouse cursor to stop strobing like a disco light between pointer and spinner modes, and once I reopen it the Permaday mod still shows as not being installed.

item.title: Can't install mods with 1.0.10
item.dc:creator: @mircearoata Mircearoata
item.description:
@mircearoata wrote:

It was an issue with one of the app’s dependencies. v1.0.11 fixes that

Read full topic
